}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "quality"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c.;"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "being dissimilar, different, diverse, various, incongruous, discordant,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "dissentient:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Axtlf", "text_ar": "اختلف"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is the"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "contr. of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Ait~afaqa", "text_ar": "اِتَّفَقَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; (K, TA;) and is said of anything that is dissimilar [in the parts or members &c. of which it is composed]; as also ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "txAlf", "text_ar": "تخالف", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (TA.) You say,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlA^amoraAni", "text_ar": "الاَمْرَانِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "txAlf", "text_ar": "تخالف", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Axtlf AlAmrAn", "text_ar": "اختلف الامران"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "], i. e."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "lamo yat~afiqaA", "text_ar": "لَمْ يَتَّفِقَا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The two things,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "affairs,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "cases, were,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "became, dissimilar,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c.]. (TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AxtlfwA", "text_ar": "اختلفوا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "txAlfwA", "text_ar": "تخالفوا", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Mgh, Msb) ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "They disagreed,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c.,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "fiY A^amorK", "text_ar": "فِى اَمْرٍ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in a thing"}, {"kind": "text